{"word":"G4741 - στηρίζω - stērízō - stay-rid'-zo - Fix","slug":"G4741","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">στηρίζω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>stērízō"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>stay-rid'-zo"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Fix"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x03C3;&#x03C4;&#x03B7;&#x03C1;&#x03B9;&#x0301;&#x03B6;&#x03C9; - ste&#x0304;rizo&#x0304;</b> - <i>stay-rid'-zo</i><p/>From a presumed derivative of <a href=\"#/G2476\">G2476</a> (like <a href=\"#/G4731\">G4731</a>); to <i>set fast</i>, that is, (literally) to <i>turn resolutely</i> in a certain direction, or (figuratively) to <i>confirm:</i> - fix, (e-) stablish, stedfastly set, strengthen."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G1991\">G1991</a>, <a href=\"#/G4740\">G4740</a>, <a href=\"#/G793\">G793</a>"}]}